chatapp_outage_mobile_message: We're sorry, we were not able to load this Chat due to an issue. For instant support, you can check out our in-app self-help options.
chatapp_outage_dialog_content: We're sorry, we were not able to load this Chat due to an issue.
chatapp_outage_dialog_subtext: For instant support, you can check out our in-app self-help options. If you are still looking for help, check us out at doordash.com/help or call us via the phone icon at the top.
chatapp_long_wait_agent_time_dialog_text: We're sorry, but we can't find an agent at this time
chatapp_long_wait_agent_time_dialog_subt: We are experiencing high demand right now. You can continue waiting for a moment or come back later.
chatapp_long_wait_times_body: We'll help you as soon as possible. Keep your chat open in the app and we'll send a push notification when an agent is available. You can also end the chat if you no longer need support.
chatapp_idle_response_body: Thanks for continuing to be patient while we help other customers. Confirm that you're still waiting so that the chat doesn't time out, or end the chat if you no longer need support.
chatapp_teammate_outage_body: Our chat support systems went down unexpectedly so we had to end the chat. Try calling us so we can get this resolved for you as soon as possible.
chatapp_chat_outage_body: Chat support is temporarily down. If you still need help, you can call us below.
chatapp_chat_throttle_outage_body: Our chat support systems went down unexpectedly so we had to end the chat. Please visit our Help Centre below for guidance.
